Class CrawlerActionRepo

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.pds.harvest.search.oodt.crawler.CrawlerActionRepo
public class CrawlerActionRepo extends Object
A repository and reader for CrawlerActions associated with Crawler lifecycle phases: preIngest, postIngestSuccess and postIngestFail.
